<div id="fraud-notifications-modal" class="ingenico-modal modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
                <h3 class="modal-title">
                    Why is it useful to receive fraud notifications?
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>Ingenico takes care of the security of your payments to avoid any fraud that can potentially damage your business.
                    </li>
                    <br>
                    <li>
                    Having this option enabled allows you to get information about suspicious orders preventively so that you could take action and cancel the delivery.
                    </li>
                    <br>
                    <li>
                    Lack of this visibility can lead to the situation of having chargebacks for the delivered orders.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    Close
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
